task.summary: Success!! Module Multithreading is awesomely working!!!
Added testmodule2, changed robot superclass to iterativerobot
Framework works now, started adding modules: 2Joysticks, BasicArcadeDrive, Cannon. Also added Event system
All Teleop output functionallity fully working: Drive, Cannon, and Intake
Added module Compressor, added DataStreams, which transfer live data from one module to another, added start of xml config file, added dry-fire protection code to the cannon.
Moved event and dataStream systems to base out of ModMaster, currently broken
lots of stuff done, config file loading now works, enhanced datastreams, refactored everything to conform to python naming conventions.
still issues, event update_arms is getting triggered from somewhere
Always more improvement! added the module.load events, as well as run events! Improved error handling. The framework is getting closer and closer to being feature-complete!
